01:07:00.265 --> 01:07:15.911
I claim this year Lord breakthroughs will happen in young people in this room and some of us who are older in this room that this year Lord we will leave behind the sins that so easily beset us and we will begin to walk in newness of life because we trust you and your word Lord.

01:07:17.213 --> 01:07:22.482
And then let your young people go home like a mighty army conquering and to conquer

01:07:22.754 --> 01:07:27.841
bringing not just their family to Christ, but their friends and neighbors as well.

01:07:27.861 --> 01:07:30.625
This is our prayer in Jesus' precious and holy name.

01:07:30.645 --> 01:07:32.768
May the church say amen and amen.

